Uses of Package
org.openstreetmap.osm

Packages that use org.openstreetmap.osm
org.openstreetmap.osm Provides basic interface to write programs that work with OpenStreetMap-data. 
org.openstreetmap.osm.Plugins Provides basic interfaces for a generic Plugin -mechanism 
org.openstreetmap.osm.data Provides basic classes for loading, saving and storing OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.h2   
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.osmbin.v1_0 This is the implementation of version 1.0 of the Osmbin file-format 
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.projection Provides basic classes for working with projections of coordinates in OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.searching Provides basic classes for searching for names and addresses in OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.osm.data.searching.advancedAddressDB This is the implementation of an advanced version of the AddressDatabase.
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman OSMNavigation provides the infrastructure required to build a navigator/route-planner on top of OpenStreetMap-data 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.gps Provides everything required to work with GPS-devices and log-files in NMEA or GPX -format 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.navigation Provides a high-level navigating-library 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.painting Provides a classes that can paint the map, route and marked points into a graphics-context 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.painting.odr   
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.routing.describers Provides classes for giving driving-instructions 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.routing.metrics Provides metrics to optimize a route for. 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.routing.routers Provides classes that do route-calculation 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.routing.selectors Provides classes that define allowed and forbidden ways to route on 
org.openstreetmap.travelingsalesman.routing.speech
